# This is my github page detailing the bluenbn project

## First update 8/07/2016
Mmmm very interesting, I think I am going to start documenting my findings here.

[Link to page1.html](https://kilaorange.github.io/bluenbn/page1.html)

### ETL component of project
There is an ETL component 
Get data from Damian (connect)
Get data from DAR SQL server
Get data from NBNCo
Get data from Peter Holmes (consumer) 
Get data from TB and enterprise
This is a data ingestion process. Quite hard to manage.
Will take input from various teams to get it working.
Data sucked into BUD for calculations

# Project Risks
The project risk is that we are relying on other teams to provide data and if they dont support us in a timely manner our project wont work.
